                                            Meier</persName> gestochen hatte,</note>
                                    vgl.
                                    4. Abt., Bd. VIII, Abb.
                            9</note></seg>.?</ref> Schreib mir was jeder
                            Ra<supplied reason="damage" cert="high">hmen</supplied> kostet<anchor type="target" xml:id="stop_m2j_n44_2nb"/></seg>
